description: Sigmund Freud is one of the most well known contributors to the field of psychiatry, pioneering the psychoanalytic school.  His theories about the unconscious mind, transference and the defense mechanism of repression are central to the study of psychology. Read all about him with this Sigmund Freud eBook.  It provides you with a truly remarkable account of this great man's life.  Starting with his early life and education, the book goes on to chronicle his greatest achievements and most important theories.  Download this title today and learn all about this fascinating man.
